snippet.title: NES Longplay [901] The Hunt for Red October
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: JagOfTroy

Having never seen the movie, I can't say how much this game does it justice. However, I do like it despite the Silver Surfer difficulty towards the later levels and unexplained ways to fight bosses. 

The last level is worth playing it, as well as the great cut-scenes. -
